## 9. Data Flow Diagrams

### Search Flow

```
[Search button click]  ← main thread
        │
        ├─ _snapshot_filter() → f
        └─ Thread(_search, f) ─────────────────────────────────┐
                                                               │ background thread
                                                               ▼
                                                    connect_db1()
                                                    cursor.execute(FailedFG.sql, ...)
                                                    rows = cursor.fetchall()
                                                         │
                                              for each row:
                                                    self.after(0, _insert_tree_row)
                                                         │
                                                         ▼
                                              [main thread inserts row into tree]
```

---

### Reprocess All Flow

```
[Reprocess All click]  ← main thread
        │
        ├─ serials = snapshot tree rows
        ├─ f = _snapshot_filter()
        └─ Thread(_reprocess_worker, serials, f, advance_queue=True)
                    │                                          background thread
                    │
            for each serial:
                ├─ skip if in self.processed
                └─ _process_fg(serial, f, cursor, session)
                        │
                        ├─ cursor.execute(AIOT03_BasedOnFG.sql, ...)
                        └─ for each message row:
                                session.post(WEB_SERVICES, payload)
                                self.result_data[serial] = {status, response}
                                self.after(0, log_message)
                    │
            _maybe_advance_sync_queue(f)
                    │
                    ├─ fetch_sync_queue_list(...)
                    ├─ find next queue
                    └─ self.after(0, _advance_on_main)
                                │               main thread
                                ├─ sync.configure(values=...)
                                ├─ sync_var.set(next_q)
                                ├─ processed.clear()
                                └─ Thread(_search, next_f).start()
```

